Khumar Episode 11 [Eng Sub] Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Feroze Khan - Neelam Muneer - 29th December 2023 - Har Pal Geo

Khumar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

Khumar is a timeless love story that delves into the challenges arising from societal class differences and the negativity that stems from them. Khumar explores the complexities of love in the face of societal expectations and challenges. Faiz and Hareem, two individuals from different backgrounds, find their lives connected by destiny.

Faiz, born into an affluent family, contrasts sharply with Hareem, who hails from a
lower-middle-class background. Despite their differences, fate weaves their paths together. Hareem, diligently working to make ends meet amid her brother Rufi's educational needs and her mother's medical expenses, faces numerous hurdles. In the midst of her struggles, Faiz, a friend of Rufi's, silently supports them financially and even gets work for Hareem, albeit discreetly.

Hareem's family doesn't know that Faiz loves her, leading to a one-sided love affair. Faiz's love for Hareem remains a secret, but his mother disapproves of his association with Hareem's family due to the significant class difference. But fate decides to play its tune, and an unexpected event turns the lives of Faiz and Hareem upside down.

What was this surprising turn of events that changed everything for Faiz and Hareem? Will the gap in their social status keep them apart? Can Faiz convince his mother to accept Hareem? If they marry, can they create a happy life together despite their different backgrounds and mindsets?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Writer: Maha Malik
Director: Ali Faizan

Cast:
Feroze Khan as Faiz
Neelam Muneer as Hareem

It's best for the night skin treatment, making your skin flawless day by day.

This specially designed overnight regenerist cream, artistically crafted for specific age groups, transforms into a potent blend of natural ceramides, peptides, vitamins, amino acids, fruit actives, flower actives, plant actives, root, and bark actives. It effectively addresses and guards against various skin conditions caused by environmental pollution, climatic disturbances, and age-related damage across diverse age groups.
It enhances natural health glow and Clears blemishes giving a youthful radiance.

snippet.title: Uppum Mulakum 2 | Flowers | EP# 420
snippet.description:
പാറമട വീട്ടുകാരെ ആശങ്കയിലാക്കി കേശു. വീട്ടിലുള്ളവരോടെല്ലാം അപചിതരെ പോലെയാണ് കേശു പെരുമാറുന്നത്. കേശുവിന്റെ ഓര്‍മ ഒരു വര്‍ഷം പിന്നിലാണെന്നാണ് രാംകുമാറിന്റെ സംശയം.

Keshu puts the entire Paramada house in panic. He treats everyone in the house like strangers. Ramkumar suspects that Keshu's memory is a year behind.

Episode 3966: Fine Dena Hoga
--------------------------------------------------------
Jetha and the other members are interested in knowing why Bhide called the meeting. When Madhavi and Bhide eventually arrive, they let everyone know that Tapu Sena was the one who requested the meeting. A discussion about the appropriate penalty for an undesirable gift breaks out, inspiring everyone to come up with original and kind gift ideas later on. Who will receive the worst gift?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3966, 28 Dec 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Nazre Ruke Jo Mujh Pe Ho Jaye Woh Deewana,

Ho Jaye Na Hungama…
Aashique Hai Saare Mere Karte Rahe Bahana ….
Chor Denge Chor Denge Hum 
Has Ke Yun Chor Denge Hum…
Dhin Tak Dhin Tak Dhin
Nacha Ke Dikha Denge Hum …

Jhatka Laga Hai Kyu Tumko ?
Tada … O Tumko Tada…. 
Matka Ke Chal Diye Hum Jo 
Khatka Hua Hai Kyu Tum Ko ?
Tada … O Tumko Tada …..

Hey Senorita 
Teri Kitni Kara Main Tareefa ?
Sunn Bonita 
Aise Door Na Ja , Kareeb Aaa…..

Main Toh Deewana Tera,
Sun Le Fasana Mera… 
Tere Liye Maine Chora Hai Sabko
Yun Toh Na Dil Ko Dukha…

Tod Denge Tod Denge Hum, 
Jo Hai Yeh Tere Bharam,
Rule Kare Jag Saara 
Aur Hum Hi Kare Hai Run ….. 

Latka Dikha Diya Tune
Jhatka Laga Hai Yun Dil Ko 
Tada O Tumko Tada…
Matka Ke Chal Diye Tu Jo
Atka Hua Hai Dil Yeh Toh
Tada O Tumko Tada….

Karti Hu Guroor
Tujhko Main Yeh Du Bata…
Deewane Door Ja 
Na Mujhko Tu Yun Sata….

Main Woh Aatish Jo Jala Du ,
Bekhayali Ka Sama Hu…
Jo Na Utre Woh Nasha Hu…
Main Woh Raaj Ek Gehra Hu…..
Jo Mita De Woh Bala Hu .. 
Main Toh Sab Ki Tamanna Hu … 

Teri Neendein Uda Du…..
Teri Shamein Saja Du…..

Latka Dikha Diya Tune
Jhatka Laga Hai Yun Dil Ko 
Tada O Tumko Tada…

Atka Hua Hai Dil Yeh Toh
Tada O Tumko Tada….

Khatka Hua Hai Kyu Tum Ko ?
Tada … O Tumko Tada …..

लड़का:- धीरे धीरे जान अनजान होत बाड़ू
मरता लईका सेयान होत बाड़ू
बोल सेनुर बनब की सिंगारे रहब
लड़की:- जब तक जियब तोहारे रहब...
शादी तोहसे नाही होइ त कुँआरे रहब....

लड़का:- सब मान जाई ना त जान जाई,ए रानी हो जा तू राजी हो
रहबु कुँआरे ना तोहरा दुआरे जानू हमार बाजा बाजी हो
लड़की:- कबो छोड़ब ना वादा ना तोड़ब ए जान तनि हमरा प राख भरोसा
बानी लाइल तू खा ल ना डोसा ए जान मुँह कर ना जइसे समोसा

लड़का:- कर ना हद,बड़ी होता दरद, बोल मरद बनब की ईयारे रहब
लड़की:- जब तक जियब तोहारे रहब...
शादी तोहसे नाही होइ त कुँआरे रहब....
पापाजी के भले दुआरे रहब शादी तोसे नाही होइ त कुँआरे रहब


लड़का :- छूटी ना प्यार परिवार भले छूटी,देखब के हमरा के बोली हो
क ल सगाई तबे तोहार आई,नीलकमल घरे डोली हो

लड़की :- काहे मनवा में फूट ता लावा, ई मोहब्बत प बा तोहरे दावा
मिली आशु दिल मे ना में जगह, केहू आई ना तोहरा अलावा
लड़का :- जवने ही रात, कह आई बारात, मयूर बान्हि खड़ा अपना कपारे रहब

लड़की :- जब तक जियब तोहारे रहब...
शादी तोहसे नाही होइ त कुँआरे रहब....

snippet.title: Living on Rs 100 for a day Ft. @nishutiwarivlogs  | Budget Checklist✅ | Pass👍 or Fail👎 | Nykaa
snippet.description:
You must’ve planned several treats and strolled to the market to buy that one accessory…but what if we say, you have to survive a day and relish the same for just Rs. 100!!🤯🤯

Welcome to another episode of Nykaa Pass👍 or Fail👎 Challenge, where we have Nishu Tiwari aka @nishutiwarivlogs with us, who is taking up the lead to participate in the fun challenge and survive with all flags. In this video, watch Nishu preparing a budget checklist and spending the money on food from breakfast to dinner and gift shopping from the market, without compromising on style and emotions.😎💖 

So, what are you waiting for? Watch the video, join the fun roller coaster ride, and let us know what will be your first picks if living on Rs.100 for 24 hours in the comments down below!!💵💲

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3965 | 27 Dec 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3965: Meeting Ka Reason
--------------------------------------------------------
When Jethalal notices Bhide has not arrived at the clubhouse, he inquires Taarak about his whereabouts. Taarak assures Jetha that he is not cognizant of Bhide. The residents of Gokuldham gradually arrive, but Bhide is nowhere to be found. Jetha and the other members are curious about the cause of Bhide's meeting. Finally, Madhavi and Bhide come, but they inform everyone that it was Tapu Sena who asked for the rendezvous.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3965, 27 Dec 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Baylagaam Mega Ep 91 - [Eng Sub] Ali Abbas - Laiba Khan - Haroon Shahid - Tuba Anwar - 28th Dec 2023
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Baylagaam Mega Ep 91 - [Eng Sub] Ali Abbas - Laiba Khan - Haroon Shahid - Tuba Anwar - 28th Dec 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

The story centers around Ramsha, a young girl and the only child of her loving parents, Sajid and Mehnaz. Raised with affection and no restrictions, Ramsha enjoys unlimited internet access, which leads to her spending an excessive time on social media, quickly becoming her hobby.
As her fascination with social media intensifies, Ramsha's hobby evolves into an all-consuming passion for fame, prompting her to take extreme measures. During her relentless pursuit of stardom, she crosses paths with Afnan, the son of the influential businessman Qasim Ali. While Afnan, who holds affection for his paternal cousin Aleezay, views Ramsha as a source of amusement, she misinterprets their friendship as love.
Disheartened by her failed search for love, Ramsha turns towards fame. Ramsha's unwavering quest for popularity propels her onto a challenging path, causing turmoil within her family. As her popularity soars, she becomes increasingly distant from her loved ones, leading her life down a tumultuous road, where she discovers the other side of fame many people are unaware of. Along this journey, she encounters Afnan once more, but circumstances have taken a different turn.
Will Ramsha achieve the fame she so desperately desires? Will her pursuit bring dire consequences? Can she find contentment in fame instead of love? And will Ramsha's parents have to bear the consequences of her passion?

Besides giving live and current information the channel broadcasts news on sports,  business and international affairs. It also offers a wide array of weekend programmes.
 
The channel is promoted by Chennai based New Gen Media Corporation. The company also publishes popular Tamil magazines - Puthiya Thalaimurai and Kalvi.

snippet.title: Real Story of Dunki | How Indians Cross US Mexico Border? | Donkey Process | Dhruv Rathee
snippet.description:
🤖 Join the Master ChatGPT - Full Course : https://academy.dhruvrathee.com/chatgpt
Learn to harness the power of ChatGPT to transform your life! 
Use coupon code: DUN40 for 40% discount! Offer only valid for the first 400 people. 

In this video by Dhruv Rathee, the focus is on the heart-wrenching story of illegal immigration from India, specifically the tragic journey of a family from the small village of Dingucha, Gujarat. The video delves into the realities of "donkey flights," a term for illegal immigration routes, and the dangerous journeys families undertake for a better life in countries like the USA ,UK and Canada. It also explores the broader context of why people risk everything, including political and economic factors, and the role of misleading agents in this perilous process. Donkey Process of illegal immigration has also inspired the story of the movie "Dunki" starring Shah Rukh Khan. Watch as Dhruv Rathee sheds light on this critical issue, blending personal stories with broader social and political insights.

snippet.title: SURPRISE DATE WITH A FAN GIRL 😍 | MOHAK NARANG
snippet.description:
You can buy this Garnier Vitamin C range from here:
https://bit.ly/3sABpsU
@garnierindia

Hi guys, hope you are doing well. 
Looking for ways to flaunt the healthy skin of your dreams this festive season? In today’s video, I’m going to reveal how to achieve spotless, bright skin in three simple steps by using Garnier vitamin C skincare products. So, without further ado, let’s get started. 

Vitamin C, being one of the most effective ingredients in the skincare industry, offers a variety of benefits to the skin. And to make the most of this ingredient, it’s crucial to include it in your skincare routine, be it as a cleanser, serum, moisturiser or more, especially when the festive season is here. So, to help you flaunt spotless, bright skin and prep it for the festive season, here’s a simple yet super effective 3-step skincare regimen to cleanse, treat and seal moisture in your skin effortlessly – 

Step 1: Start by cleansing your face with the Garnier Bright Complete Face Wash to get rid of dirt, dust, oil, sebum, and impurities. Apply the face wash on wet face and massage gently, avoiding the eye contour area. The vitamin C face wash helps reduce dullness and restore your glowing, healthy-looking complexion. It also helps lessen dark spots and acne marks in just a few days, while leaving the skin feel bright. The Garnier Vitamin C face wash is gentle on the skin and suitable for all skin types. 

Step 2: Next, using the dropper take out a pea-sized amount of the Garnier Vitamin C Serum and apply it on cleansed skin. Dab the Garnier face serum all over your face and neck using small, gentle tapping motions. Enriched with 30X vitamin C, the Garnier serum fades dark spots and dull skin in just three days. It is made with a combination of vitamin C, niacinamide and salicylic acid to give your skin an instant boost of freshness and brightness. The lightweight and non-oily formula instantly penetrates the skin and makes it feel super comfortable all day long. The vitamin C face serum is available in four different sizes for you to choose from and is formulated without sulphates and parabens. 

Step 3: Finish off your three-step vitamin C routine by applying the Garnier Bright Complete Serum Cream evenly on your face and neck. The Garnier Serum Cream is made with a two-in-one formulation that helps you achieve the best of both worlds. It easily penetrates the deepest level of the skin and shields it from signs of sun damage such as skin tanning, dark spots, and sunburn. This cream also lightens dark spots, brightens skin, and evens skin tone. 

These products are definitely a game-changer for me. Highly recommended! So, what are you waiting for? Grab your hands on the Garnier vitamin C skincare products right away to #CleanseTreatSeal your skin on the go this festive season. 

I hope you found this video helpful and if you did, don’t forget to like, share, and subscribe to my channel for more such videos. Also, let me know your thoughts in the comments below.  
Thank you for watching, see you soon!
